item.title: CVE-2023-4216|2024-08-02T07:17:12.248Z -- unknown -- orders%20tracking%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The Orders Tracking for WooCommerce WordPress plugin before 1.2.6 doesn't validate the file_url parameter when importing a CSV file, allowing high privilege users with the manage_woocommerce capability to access any file on the web server via a Traversal attack. The content retrieved is however limited to the first line of the file.
